  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds:
    - rid: 2042809312053297233
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-1
        text: "So\u2026 someone actually followed the trail."
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-2
    - rid: 2042809312053297234
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-2
        text: Good. That means the clues still work.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-3
    - rid: 2042809312053297235
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-3
        text: Don't worry. You're not in danger. If I wanted to stay hidden, you
          wouldn't have found this place.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-4
    - rid: 2042809312053297236
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-4
        text: I made that trail to test something.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-5
    - rid: 2042809312053297237
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-5
        text: "Heroes are dangerous things. People worship them, write songs about
          them\u2026 and then forget them the moment they disappear."
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-6
    - rid: 2042809312053297238
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-6
        text: I learned that the hard way.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-7
    - rid: 2042809312053297239
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-7
        text: He pauses for a moment and sighs.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-8
    - rid: 2042809312053297240
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-8
        text: So I stopped being a hero.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-9
    - rid: 2042809312053297241
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-9
        text: "Now I just\u2026 make sure this island keeps running, but qeuitly."
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-10
    - rid: 2042809312053297242
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-10
        text: But I can't be everywhere.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-11
    - rid: 2042809312053297243
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-11
        text: "Which is why I needed to know if someone out there was curious enough\u2026
          stubborn enough\u2026 to follow the trail."
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-12
    - rid: 2042809312053297244
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-12
        text: He looks over at the players ship
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-13
    - rid: 2042809312053297245
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-13
        text: You travel by the stars, don't you?
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-14
    - rid: 2042809312053297246
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-14
        text: Then maybe you can help with something bigger than this island.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-15
    - rid: 2042809312053297247
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-15
        text: Ships have been disappearing lately.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-16
    - rid: 2042809312053297248
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-16
        text: Not storms. Not pirates.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-17
    - rid: 2042809312053297249
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-17
        text: Something stranger.
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-18
    - rid: 2042809312053297250
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-18
        text: "If you're willing\u2026 I need someone who can sail further than I
          can."
        nextNodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-19
    - rid: 2042809312053297251
      type: {class: DialogueLineNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        nodeID: UnkownHeroQuest6-19
        text: Follow the stars. See what you find.
        nextNodeID: 
